    <title>hexo添加网易云音乐</title>
    <url>/2018/06/17/hexo%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E7%BD%91%E6%98%93%E4%BA%91%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>1、登录网易云音乐官网，首先要检查的是音乐是否有版权限制，如果有版权限制，则无法生成外链。</p>
<p><img src="/.xyz//image-20200316202941005.png" alt="image-20200316202941005"></p>
<p>选择一首没有版权保护，而且是你喜欢的歌曲，<a href="https://music.163.com/#/outchain/2/167850/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">点击</a>左边生成外链播放器。</p>
<p><img src="/.xyz//image-20200316203443756.png" alt="image-20200316203443756"></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">iframe</span> <span class="attr">frameborder</span>=<span class="string">"no"</span> <span class="attr">border</span>=<span class="string">"0"</span> <span class="attr">marginwidth</span>=<span class="string">"0"</span> <span class="attr">marginheight</span>=<span class="string">"0"</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">330</span> <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">86</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&amp;id=167850&amp;auto=1&amp;height=66"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">iframe</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>2、打开next主题文件目录，找到sidebar.swig文件</p>
<p><img src="/.xyz//image-20200316204138560.png" alt="image-20200316204138560"></p>
]]></content>
